{"tid":2086001,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人用過a**x w**g career coaching? 係咪伏黎","createTime":"2020-06-30T06:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T14:08:32.000Z","uid":360601,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"985eaed7c2013cb8c6019b522ce868396202ea51","tid":2086001,"uid":360601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"coach學生入投行front office過d<br />\n<br />\n睇之前連登好多人講過佢<br />\n我睇d post都覺得好恐怖，點解可以收費咁高 <br />\n好似要收誠意金20k，之後成功搵到工就要收你第一個月既intern salary，成功攞到return offer就收埋你頭一個月既full time salary 如果係bb front office咁樣已經十幾萬 好似好貪心咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔知我information係咪真，如果知道真實情況既人可以share下<br />\n<br />\n我呢排有個friend話呢個coach主動approach過佢，之後叫佢填survey，phone interview，之後face to face interview....佢真係咁有料咩？<br />\n<br />\n個coach話自己係某BB行同mbb行既alumni（前者做唔夠一年，後者做左幾年）。第一係無辦法verify佢既工作經歷係咪真。第二，就算係真，佢呢d經驗已經係十幾年前既事，即係代表佢已經好多年無社會實踐經歷.....佢technical industry insights真係夠勁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都唔知實際幫到學生幾多...有少少食水feel<br />\n<br />\n點解咁多人會去報佢，有無人可以講下<br />\n<br />\nhkcar***s 呢間野都可以講下"},{"pid":"946ba6d036600dc0681484a7c4d26e881a0632f0","tid":2086001,"uid":5477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T06:44:28.000Z","msg":"聽日 2pm 東角道集合<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5KnaBXr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5KnaBXr.jpg&h=cd06e4f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5ohgXs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5ohgXs.jpg&h=032359c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y8Vjvhs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy8Vjvhs.jpg&h=13f3b7df&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ShaBXs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ShaBXs.jpg&h=9d9ad546&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7jw3cvO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.li